originalSql:
WITH MovieDetails AS (
    SELECT 
        t.title AS movie_title,
        t.production_year,
        STRING_AGG(a.name, ', ') AS actors,
        STRING_AGG(c.kind, ', ') AS company_types,
        STRING_AGG(k.keyword, ', ') AS keywords
    FROM 
        aka_title t
    JOIN 
        cast_info ci ON t.id = ci.movie_id
    JOIN 
        aka_name a ON ci.person_id = a.person_id
    JOIN 
        movie_companies mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id
    JOIN 
        company_type c ON mc.company_type_id = c.id
    JOIN 
        movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id
    JOIN 
        keyword k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id
    GROUP BY 
        t.id, t.title, t.production_year
),
FilteredMovies AS (
    SELECT 
        movie_title,
        production_year,
        actors,
        company_types,
        keywords
    FROM 
        MovieDetails
    WHERE 
        production_year >= 2000 AND
        LOWER(actors) LIKE '%john%' 
)
SELECT 
    movie_title,
    production_year,
    actors,
    company_types,
    keywords
FROM 
    FilteredMovies
ORDER BY 
    production_year DESC

SELECT COALESCE("MOVIE_TITLE", "MOVIE_TITLE") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "PRODUCTION_YEAR", "ACTORS", "COMPANY_TYPES", "KEYWORDS"
FROM (SELECT MIN("aka_title"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "aka_title"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", LISTAGG("aka_name"."name", ', ') AS "ACTORS", LISTAGG("company_type"."kind", ', ') AS "COMPANY_TYPES", LISTAGG("keyword"."keyword", ', ') AS "KEYWORDS"
FROM "aka_title"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_title"."id" = "cast_info"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "aka_name" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "aka_title"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "company_type" ON "movie_companies"."company_type_id" = "company_type"."id"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "aka_title"."id" = "s1"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "keyword" ON "s1"."keyword_id" = "keyword"."id"
GROUP BY "aka_title"."id", "aka_title"."title", "aka_title"."production_year") AS "t2"
WHERE "t2"."PRODUCTION_YEAR" >= 2000 AND LOWER("t2"."ACTORS") LIKE '%john%'
ORDER BY "PRODUCTION_YEAR" DESC NULLS FIRST

SELECT COALESCE("id", "id") AS "id", "keyword", "phonetic_code"
FROM "keyword"

SELECT COALESCE("MOVIE_TITLE", "MOVIE_TITLE") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "PRODUCTION_YEAR", "ACTORS", "COMPANY_TYPES", "KEYWORDS"
FROM (SELECT MIN("aka_title"."title") AS "MOVIE_TITLE", "aka_title"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", LISTAGG("aka_name"."name", ', ') AS "ACTORS", LISTAGG("company_type"."kind", ', ') AS "COMPANY_TYPES", LISTAGG("s1"."keyword", ', ') AS "KEYWORDS"
FROM "aka_title"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "aka_title"."id" = "cast_info"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "aka_name" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."person_id"
INNER JOIN "movie_companies" ON "aka_title"."id" = "movie_companies"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "company_type" ON "movie_companies"."company_type_id" = "company_type"."id"
INNER JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "aka_title"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "movie_keyword"."keyword_id" = "s1"."id"
GROUP BY "aka_title"."id", "aka_title"."title", "aka_title"."production_year") AS "t2"
WHERE "t2"."PRODUCTION_YEAR" >= 2000 AND LOWER("t2"."ACTORS") LIKE '%john%'
ORDER BY "PRODUCTION_YEAR" DESC NULLS FIRST
